---
import "../styles/global.css";
import LandingNavbar from "../components/landing/LandingNavbar.astro";
import LandingFooter from "../components/landing/LandingFooter.astro";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Terms of Service | Xeni</title>
    <meta name="description" content="Terms of Service for Xeni AI Content Automation platform. Read our usage rules, agreements, and policies." />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:ital,opsz,wght@0,9..144,300..900;1,9..144,300..900&family=Geist:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/@tabler/icons-webfont@latest/dist/tabler-icons.min.css" />
  </head>
  <body class="bg-[#F8F9FB] text-[#111827] font-sans antialiased">
    <LandingNavbar />

    <main class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-20 overflow-x-hidden">
      <!-- Header Section -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex justify-center mb-4">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center px-3 py-1 rounded-full border border-gray-300 bg-transparent text-[11px] font-semibold text-[#667085] uppercase tracking-wider whitespace-nowrap font-geist">
            Legal & Compliance
          </span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-[36px] md:text-[48px] font-normal text-[#111827] font-fraunces tracking-tight leading-tight mb-4">
          Terms of Service
        </h1>
        <p class="text-[13px] md:text-[14px] text-[#667085] font-medium font-geist">
          Last Updated: June 19, 2026
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- Main Policy Container -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-[2rem] p-8 md:p-12 shadow-[0_8px_30px_rgba(0,0,0,0.01)] font-geist">
          
          <!-- Summary/TOC Checklist Box -->
          <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-2xl p-6 mb-10">
            <h3 class="text-[14px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-3 uppercase tracking-wider">Quick Navigation</h3>
            <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-3 text-[13px] text-[#4B5563]">
              <a href="#acceptance" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-checklist"></i> 1. Acceptance of Terms
              </a>
              <a href="#accounts" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-user-cog"></i> 2. Account Registration
              </a>
              <a href="#services-scope" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-rocket"></i> 3. Services & Usage Limits
              </a>
              <a href="#third-parties" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-brand-meta"></i> 4. Third-Party Integrations
              </a>
              <a href="#intellectual-property" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-license"></i> 5. Intellectual Property
              </a>
              <a href="#billing" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-credit-card"></i> 6. Billing & Cancellations
              </a>
              <a href="#liability" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-alert-triangle"></i> 7. Liability & Warranties
              </a>
              <a href="#governing-law" class="hover:text-[#111827] flex items-center gap-2 font-medium transition-colors">
                <i class="ti ti-gavel"></i> 8. Governing Law
              </a>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- Document Content -->
          <div class="space-y-10 text-[14px] leading-relaxed text-[#4B5563]">
            
            <!-- Section 1 -->
            <section id="acceptance" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">01.</span> Acceptance of Terms
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                These Terms of Service ("Terms") constitute a legally binding agreement between you ("User", "you", "your") and Xeni (operated by <strong class="text-[#111827]">PT PERSONA DIGITAL KREATIF</strong>, referred to as "we", "us", "our") regarding your access to and use of our content automation platform, software, websites, and related integrations.
              </p>
              <p>
                By registering an account, purchasing a subscription, or accessing any element of the Services, you agree to be bound by these Terms and our Privacy Policy. If you do not agree to these Terms, you are prohibited from using the platform and must terminate your account immediately.
              </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 2 -->
            <section id="accounts" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">02.</span> Account Registration & Security
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                To access features of the platform, you must register for a user account. You agree to:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li>Provide accurate, current, and complete details during sign-up.</li>
                <li>Maintain the confidentiality and security of your access credentials.</li>
                <li>Accept full responsibility for all activities, actions, and transactions executed under your account credentials.</li>
                <li>Notify our support team immediately at <a href="mailto:contact@xenilabs.app" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">contact@xenilabs.app</a> upon discovering unauthorized access or security breaches.</li>
              </ul>
              <p>
                We reserve the right, in our sole discretion, to suspend or terminate accounts that violate our community guidelines, contain fraudulent details, or infringe upon third-party rights.
              </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 3 -->
            <section id="services-scope" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">03.</span> Platform Services & Usage Limits
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Xeni operates an AI-assisted marketing automation service that generates captions, designs visual layouts, models brand guidelines (Business DNA), and hosts scheduling tools.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Your subscription tier determines your active limits, including active AI Agents, Generation Credits, and Brand DNA slots:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li><strong class="text-[#111827]">Generation Credits:</strong> Deducted upon each successful invocation of caption generators, visual planners, or content pipelines. Unused credits do not roll over to the subsequent billing cycle unless explicitly specified in your plan description.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-[#111827]">Fair Use:</strong> You agree not to overload our hosting infrastructure or run high-frequency automated scraping scripts on our backend APIs. We reserve the right to temporarily throttle database request volume for accounts showing anomalous traffic patterns.</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 4 -->
            <section id="third-parties" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">04.</span> Third-Party Platform Integrations
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Our Services allow you to connect your account to third-party social networks (specifically Meta/Facebook, Instagram, Google, and X/Twitter) via official OAuth APIs to enable publishing.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-4">
                When using these integrations, you agree that:
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li>You will adhere to the respective developer guidelines, policies, and community terms of those networks (e.g., the Meta Platform Terms, Instagram Community Guidelines).</li>
                <li>Xeni has no authority, oversight, or control over the operational status, content moderation actions, or policy enforcement decisions of integrated networks.</li>
                <li>We are not liable for any interruptions, channel disconnects, account suspension, or content removal occurring on third-party channels due to posts published through our platform.</li>
                <li>You can sever OAuth integrations directly at any time inside our console or from your third-party account dashboard.</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 5 -->
            <section id="intellectual-property" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">05.</span> Intellectual Property & Content Ownership
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                <strong class="text-[#111827]">Our Platform:</strong> Xeni, including all logos, layout UI designs, graphic elements, databases, codebases, and intellectual assets, remains the exclusive property of Xeni and is protected under national copyright laws and international treaties.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-4">
                <strong class="text-[#111827]">Your Content:</strong> You retain full copyright and ownership of all raw texts, assets, logos, brand guides (Business DNA), and information inputs uploaded to the console.
              </p>
              <p>
                <strong class="text-[#111827]">AI Outputs:</strong> To the extent permitted by applicable laws, you own the creative outputs generated by our AI workflows (captions, graphic templates). You grant Xeni a worldwide, royalty-free, non-exclusive license to process, cache, and transmit your inputs and generated results solely as required to provide our content planning services.
              </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 6 -->
            <section id="billing" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">06.</span> Billing, Subscriptions & Cancellations
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Subscription payments are processed on a recurring pre-paid basis (monthly or annually) via Stripe.
              </p>
              <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 mb-4">
                <li><strong class="text-[#111827]">Automatic Renewal:</strong> Your plan automatically renews at the end of each billing cycle unless you cancel the renewal before the next cycle date.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-[#111827]">Cancellations:</strong> You can terminate your active subscription renewal at any time directly through your dashboard Billing portal. Upon cancellation, you retain premium access until the end of your prepaid period.</li>
                <li><strong class="text-[#111827]">Refunds:</strong> All payments are non-refundable unless required by regional legislation or in the case of system billing errors validated by our support desk.</li>
              </ul>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 7 -->
            <section id="liability" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">07.</span> Disclaimer of Warranties & Limitation of Liability
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                THE SERVICES ARE PROVIDED ON AN "AS IS" AND "AS AVAILABLE" BASIS, WITHOUT WARRANTIES OF ANY KIND, EITHER EXPRESS OR IMPLIED. TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW, XENI DISCLAIMS ALL WARRANTIES, INCLUDING MERCHANTABILITY, FITNESS FOR A PARTICULAR PURPOSE, AND NON-INFRINGEMENT.
              </p>
              <p>
                XENI SHALL NOT BE HELD LIABLE FOR INDIRECT, INCIDENTAL, SPECIAL, OR CONSEQUENTIAL DAMAGES (INCLUDING LOSS OF PROFITS, REVENUES, DATA INTEGRATION CHANNELS, OR BUSINESS STANDING) ARISING OUT OF YOUR ACCESS TO OR INABILITY TO USE THE SERVICES. OUR AGGREGATE LIABILITY FOR ALL CLAIMS RELATING TO THE SERVICES SHALL NOT EXCEED THE AMOUNT PAID BY YOU TO XENI IN THE TWELVE (12) MONTHS PRECEDING THE CLAIM EVENT.
              </p>
            </section>

            <!-- Section 8 -->
            <section id="governing-law" class="scroll-mt-24">
              <h2 class="text-[18px] font-bold text-[#111827] mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
                <span class="text-[#9CA3AF] font-light">08.</span> Governing Law & Disputes
              </h2>
              <p class="mb-4">
                These Terms and any dispute arising from your use of the platform shall be governed by, and construed in accordance with, the laws of the <strong class="text-[#111827]">Republic of Indonesia</strong>, without regard to conflict of law principles.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-4">
                Any legal actions or proceedings related to these Terms must be filed in the competent courts of <strong class="text-[#111827]">Jakarta, Indonesia</strong>, and you consent to the personal jurisdiction of such courts.
              </p>
              <p class="mb-4">
                If you have any questions or require support regarding these Terms, please contact us:
              </p>
              <div class="bg-gray-50 border border-gray-100 rounded-xl p-5 inline-block">
                <p class="font-bold text-[#111827] text-[13px] uppercase tracking-wider mb-2">Legal Operations</p>
                <p class="text-[#4B5563] text-[13px]">Email: <a href="mailto:contact@xenilabs.app" class="text-blue-600 hover:underline">contact@xenilabs.app</a></p>
                <p class="text-[#4B5563] text-[13px] mt-1">PT PERSONA DIGITAL KREATIF</p>
              </div>
            </section>

          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </main>

    <LandingFooter />
  </body>
</html>
